As you explore Rath Cail, you have encountered a number of ravening carrion-flies. Unlike the more docile ones you have encountered near the foetid pools of Lhingris, these are seemingly content to prey on the living as well as the dead.\n\nYou should defeat many of the ravening carrion-flies and make clear the way through Rath Cail.
Ravening carrion-flies can be found in Rath Cail.\n\nYou have been beset by ravening carrion-flies in Rath Cail and should defeat them to make clear the way deeper into Lhingris.
